Due to a little thing called work, have to take a vacation day today to do all this. Because DMV conveniently only open work hours.
Get different person this time. Nope. Can't complete transaction. Need to go through DEQ first.
Tues: Go to DMV. Explain situation. They say fill out this form and pay $86 cash. I step out of line, get cash. Complete form. Back in line.
